DESCRIPTION:Stewart Nutting presents a story-led stand-up show about nihili
 sm\, burnout and the strange things we choose to care about anyway. Through
  personal stories and quietly absurd observations\, he explores what it mea
 ns to live in a world that often feels meaningless - and why we still find 
 ourselves defending small joys\, pointless efforts and moments of whimsy. T
 houghtful\, slightly bleak\, and unexpectedly warm\, this is comedy about o
 verthinking life\, questioning everything\, and discovering that even if no
 thing matters... it somehow still does.\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app
 /comedy-atlas/event/nutting-really-matters/
